VERSION 0.99.1
------------------------
   o Added Machima2() for symmetric epigenomic matrices
     (X_Epi ~ G * H_Sym * t(G), where G = T * W_RNA)
   o Added init_W_RNA, init_H_RNA, init_H_Sym params to Machima2()
     for user-supplied initialization (two-stage workflows)
   o Added fixH_Sym param to Machima2()
   o Added nmf_init_n_restart, nmf_init_num_iter, nmf_init_algorithm
     params to control internal NMF initialization
   o Fixed .returnBestNMF to support configurable restarts/iter/algorithm
   o Exported Mat2List() for splitting stacked matrices into per-group lists
   o Fixed BetaDivergence formula for Beta != 0, 1, 2
     (operator precedence bug and X/Y swap)
   o Fixed L1_W_RNA parameter being unused in W_RNA updates
   o Removed dead code in orthogonal H_RNA update
   o Fixed horizontal mode RecError to match optimization objective
   o Extracted shared cell type matching logic (.estimateCelltypes)
   o Added plot.new to NAMESPACE imports

VERSION 0.99.0
------------------------
   o Package released
